Some of the factual knowledge encoded in this package — which column headings a
given Swiss bank uses in its CSV exports, in which languages, and in which
order — was informed by the publicly available import scripts published by
Banana.ch SA:

    https://github.com/BananaAccounting/Switzerland
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
    http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

No source code from that project is reproduced here. This package is an
independent implementation with a different architecture, written in PHP.
The acknowledgement is made because the observable file formats of a number of
banks were cross-checked against that work.
